@startuml trips-iteration-8-shopping-flow
!theme plain
title Shopping List -- Command Flow (Design-Level EventStorming)

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam activityBorderColor #333333
skinparam activityBackgroundColor #FFD700
skinparam noteBorderColor #333333

|#LightBlue| Organizer
|#LightGreen| ShoppingListService
|#Gold| ShoppingList Aggregate
|#LightCoral| Persistence

== Generierung ==

|Organizer|
:GenerateShoppingListCommand
(tenantId, tripId);

|ShoppingListService|
:Lade MealPlan fuer Trip;
:Filtere Slots:
status==PLANNED && recipeId!=null;
:Lade Recipes per RecipeIds;
:Lade Trip (participantCount);

note right
  **Skalierung**:
  scaleFactor = participantCount / recipe.servings
  scaledQty = ingredient.qty * scaleFactor
end note

:Aggregiere Ingredients:
(name+unit) case-insensitive -> Mengen summieren;
:Erstelle List<ScaledIngredient>;

|ShoppingList Aggregate|
:ShoppingList.generate(
  tenantId, tripId,
  participantCount,
  recipeItems);

note right #Orange
  **ShoppingListGenerated**
  (Domain Event)
end note

|Persistence|
:repository.save(shoppingList);

== Manuelle Items ==

|#LightSkyBlue| Participant
:AddManualItemCommand
(tripId, name, qty, unit);

|ShoppingListService|
:Lade ShoppingList fuer Trip;

|ShoppingList Aggregate|
:shoppingList.addManualItem(
  name, qty, unit);
:Neues ShoppingItem(
  source=MANUAL,
  status=OPEN);

note right #Orange
  **ManualItemAdded**
end note

|Persistence|
:repository.save(shoppingList);

== Assignment ==

|Participant|
:AssignShoppingItemCommand
(tripId, itemId, memberId);

|ShoppingListService|
:Lade ShoppingList fuer Trip;

|ShoppingList Aggregate|
:shoppingList.assignItem(
  itemId, memberId);

note left
  **Invariante INV-5**:
  Item.status muss OPEN sein
end note

:Item.status = ASSIGNED
Item.assignedTo = memberId;

note right #Orange
  **ShoppingItemAssigned**
end note

|Persistence|
:repository.save(shoppingList);

== Einkauf ==

|Participant|
:MarkItemPurchasedCommand
(tripId, itemId, memberId);

|ShoppingListService|
:Lade ShoppingList fuer Trip;

|ShoppingList Aggregate|
:shoppingList.markPurchased(
  itemId, memberId);

note left
  **Invariante INV-7**:
  Item.status==ASSIGNED
  Item.assignedTo==memberId
end note

:Item.status = PURCHASED;

note right #Orange
  **ShoppingItemPurchased**
end note

|Persistence|
:repository.save(shoppingList);

== Regenerierung ==

|Organizer|
:RegenerateShoppingListCommand
(tenantId, tripId);

|ShoppingListService|
:Lade aktuelle ShoppingList;
:Berechne neue RECIPE-Items
(gleicher Algorithmus wie Generierung);

|ShoppingList Aggregate|
:shoppingList.regenerate(
  newRecipeItems);

note right
  **Regel**:
  RECIPE-Items loeschen + neu erzeugen
  MANUAL-Items bleiben erhalten
  (inkl. ASSIGNED/PURCHASED Status)
end note

note right #Orange
  **ShoppingListRegenerated**
end note

|Persistence|
:repository.save(shoppingList);

@enduml
